{"title":"灯下谣","authors":["李株"],"dates":[{"year":1947,"month":9,"day":5}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"灯下谣"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"李株"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"窗格格外面月亮一片银，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"窗里静悄悄好象没有人，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一条麻绳儿一根针，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一盏油灯儿守到更深。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"张家的丈夫李家的亲，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"咱村的好子弟都在八路军，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"子弟兵打仗为保翻身；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"咱做军鞋不为别人。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"直到那月移树稍更儿深，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"直到那稔子点完油耗尽，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"做成那毛毛底底牛鼻鼻，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"千针万针，针针儿紧。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一只军鞋捎带一道信："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——“穿上这鞋来记起人民心："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"快马加鞭往前提，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一股劲打走那顽固军！”"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":4,"page_end":4}